snippet.title: EarthBound Commercial
snippet.description:
The US commercial of EarthBound, a great game for the SNES.

 Honestly, this was awful. Who the hell names their character "NessA?!" And they should of put in a battle scene in.

The commercial sucks. The game is kicks ass though.
